{"tid":642578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[創科局]審計署：龜速累事？30%政府WiFi通勁少人用","createTime":"2018-04-26T01:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T05:23:10.000Z","uid":54733,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"57a02441d647a5940bf489289ee8f3e5cf8adc73","tid":642578,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:28:36.000Z","msg":"耗資2.85億港元的「政府WiFi通」反應極差！最新一份審計報告顯示，截至去年12月31日，全港共有616個WiFi通場地中，日均少於15人使用的場地由2009年至2012年的108個，急增至2014年至2017年間的196個，大約佔總數的3成。換言之，政府WiFi數量在過去十年雖不斷增加，卻未能鼓勵市民多加使用。 <br />\n<br />\n市民不用政府WiFi的原因可能與其龜速上網有關，政府在2016年施政報告曾承諾將「WiFi通」的連線速度提高1倍，達到每名用戶每秒3至4兆比特。不過，根據政府資訊科技總監辦公室去年就「WiFi通」服務進行周年服務檢查，涵蓋3087個熱點、涉及605個場地，發現有1171個熱點、涉及366個場地的下載速度低於每秒3兆比特。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/mobile/bkn-20180425122551538-0425_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180425%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180425122551538-0425_00822_001.html&d=lZTbtb35zidcig6EcEc214sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=d2057c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180425/mobile/bkn-20180425122551538-0425_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f96e10078a13f4ea229a3b6650c954b8475e16e8","tid":642578,"uid":61864,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"好多時自己手機都有得上網嗰陣，點解要用政府個wi-fi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2684f52fa3334ae193d321a0a2652641f23b22de","tid":642578,"uid":51134,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多時自己手機都有得上網嗰陣，點解要用政府個wi-fi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個無限data咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你喺自修室上網都要連wifi啦"},{"pid":"9f75cc40bb88fe084f5e63a9d9c84ae410e5ec6f","tid":642578,"uid":30708,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f96e10078a13f4ea229a3b6650c954b8475e16e8","tid":642578,